dc_description_s: This is the final deliverable for the Version 1 Statewide Parcel Map Database Project (V1). This feature class represents a comprehensive, spatially referenced collection of parcel geometries as recognized by local-level governments within the state of Wisconsin (aggregated from county level and municipal-level data). See the project interim report for further details on the project, the parcel layer and attributes included. https://www.sco.wisc.edu/pubs/v1-interim-report-digital-appendices/   Schema documentationcan be found here: https://www.sco.wisc.edu/parcels/data/assets/V1/V1_Parcels_Schema_Documentation.pdf    Change log and known issues can be found here: https://www.sco.wisc.edu/parcels/data/assets/Wisconsin_Statewide_Parcels_Change_Log.pdf
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
